An image URL such as 

{code}
!http://www.lulu.com/author/display_thumbnail.php?fCID=383343&fSize=zoom_!
{code} 

is rendered as 

{code}
!http://www.lulu.com/author/display_thumbnail.php?fCID=383343&amp;fSize=zoom_! 
{code}

The ampersand separating the parameter is escaped and breaks the URL.

While the image is rendered it ignores the parameter fsize=zoom.

